  "texts": [
    "In the interviews, we tried to understand the nature of social media recommendations from the participants' responses.",
    "Most users said they regularly come across various unfamiliar content, although the content suggestions generally matched their interest, but not always.",
    "The participants stated they would like to know why they came across recommended content types in both classes.",
    "One of the participants said, Often, I get suggestions of various Facebook groups.",
    "However, there is some content that I did not even search in Facebook but I can see them in my homepage."
  ],
